OL,3,CVisually impaired man is 'risking his
OL,4,Clife' after city's redevelopment
OL,6,FA visually impaired man says he is
OL,7,F'risking his life' every time he walks
OL,8,Fthrough a city centre multi-million
OL,9,Fpound redevelopment.
OL,11,FDave Steele, who has tunnel vision and
OL,12,Fhas been losing his sight for the past
OL,13,F10 years, claims concrete blocks
OL,14,Fplaced around Stevenson Square in
OL,15,FManchester's Northern Quarter, have
OL,16,Fmade his walks almost inaccessible.
