OL,6,FManchester City Council described it
OL,7,Fas "a safe space to move through."
OL,9,FDisability activists also say a lack
OL,10,Fof indicators to help when crossing
OL,11,Fthe road also pose a problem for those
OL,12,Fwho are visually impaired.
OL,14,F"Normally I'd be looking for a
OL,15,Fspinning cone, which that one's not
OL,16,Fthere," Mr Steele added.
OL,18,F"If someone's trying to get across
OL,19,Fwith a wheelchair, or who's got
OL,20,Fmobility issues, they'd be struggling
OL,21,Fto get across in time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
