OL,6,F"There's no audio whatsoever, so
OL,7,Fyou're really struggling. You're not
OL,8,Fgoing to get across safely."
OL,10,FThe control of the crossing lights,
OL,11,Fand their operation, falls under
OL,12,FTransport for Greater Manchester
OL,13,F(TfGM).
OL,15,FCampaigners are asking for those with
OL,16,Fdisabilities to be consulted when it
OL,17,Fcomes to these shared spaces.
