OL,6,F"But when you end up with places like
OL,7,Fthis that just aren't safe, you just
OL,8,Fend up not coming and avoiding the
OL,9,Farea."
OL,11,FManchester City Council say Stevenson
OL,12,FSquare is not finished yet, and they
OL,13,Fare working with access groups to
OL,14,Fensure everyone can safely use the
OL,15,Fspace.JIts statement went on to say:
OL,16,F"As with any major infrastructure
OL,17,Fworks there will be a period where any
OL,18,Fidentified issues with the final
OL,19,Fdesign and finish can be rectified
OL,20,Fbefore it is fully signed off.
